nodes.title: Control Net
nodes.description:
Generates images using Stable Diffusion with ControlNet for additional image control.
    image, controlnet, generative, stable diffusion, high-resolution, SD

    This node makes it explicit that it consumes an input image and a separate
    control image.

properties.name: loras
properties.title: Loras
properties.description: List of LoRA models to apply

properties.name: image
properties.title: Image
properties.description: Canny edge detection image for ControlNet

properties.name: strength
properties.title: Strength
properties.description: Strength of ControlNet (used for both low and high resolution)

nodes.title: Flux Kontext (Img2Img)

properties.name: model

properties.name: input_image

properties.description: Reference image for Flux Kontext img2img.

nodes.title: Lo RASelector
nodes.description:
Selects up to 5 LoRA models to apply to a Stable Diffusion model.
    lora, model customization, fine-tuning

    Use cases:
    - Combining multiple LoRA models for unique image styles
    - Fine-tuning Stable Diffusion models with specific attributes
    - Experimenting with different LoRA combinations
